definitions.definition: A suburb of the borough of Richmond upon Thames , in south-west Greater London , historically in Middlesex on the north side of the River Thames (but actually west of it) ( OS grid ref TQ1671 ) .
A village and civil parish in Tewkesbury district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref SO9633 ) .
A small settlement on Lyttelton Harbour , Canterbury , New Zealand .
